These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-1::.
5 different pets are kept: rat, horse, bird, guinea-pig, frog
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: december, january, may, july, june
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the rat is in the middle##1
7. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |   5    |
| Pet   | horse | bird | rat | frog | guinea-pig |
| Birthday   | june    | december | may     | july       | january  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-2::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski, taxi, bike, trike
House: modern, victorian, cape-cod, colonial, gothic-revival
1. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the left of the victorian house##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person driving the boat is in the middle##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is the cape-cod house##1
6. the gothic-revival house is the person driving the trike##1
7. the colonial house is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |      3      |    4     |   5    |
| Transport      | jet-ski | taxi | boat | bike | trike |
| House   | cape-cod  | colonial   | modern       | victorian    | gothic-revival   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-3::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: ivory, emerald, black, coral, chestnut
City: boston, london, nizza, miami, hamburg
1. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
2. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
3. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
4. the person who likes black is on the far left##1
5. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
6. the person who likes emerald is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Color        | black | coral | emerald | ivory | chestnut |
| City   | london  | boston      | hamburg | nizza | miami      |

