.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-4::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, pall-mall, game, chaman, blend
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: water-polo, handball, tennis, swimming, weightlifting
1. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
2. the game-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
4. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the game-smoker##1
6. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far right##1
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3    |    4    |     5     |
| Cigar   | chaman    | bluemaster        | game | pall-mall | blend |
| Sport     | water-polo | swimming | weightlifting  | handball   | tennis |

