.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-5::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  accountant, pilot, designer, freelancer, firefighter
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: rose, marigold, bellflower, tulip, daffodil
1. the person who growstulip is on the right of the designer##1
2. the person who growsmarigold is the firefighter##1
3. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the freelancer##1
4. the person who growsbellflower is in the middle##1
5. the designer is on the left of the accountant##1
6. the person who growsdaffodil is the freelancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3     |       4       |     5      |
| Job    | designer   | accountant     | pilot   | freelancer         | firefighter |
| Flower   | rose | tulip | bellflower | daffodil | marigold     |

