.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-6::.
5 different games are played: scrabble, domino, billiard, snooker, canasta
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: drama, documentary, animation, time-travel, satire
1. the person watching time-travel movies is in the middle##1
2. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
4. the person watching animation movies is the person playing billiard##1
5. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing domino##1
6. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |     5     |
| Game       | snooker   | billiard   | domino | canasta | scrabble |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | animation | time-travel   | satire | drama       |

