.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-7::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: mirinda, juice, milk, coffee, cola
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: time-travel, martial-arts, documentary, disaster, epic
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is in the middle##1
6. the person watching documentary movies is the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5      |
| Beverage     | juice   | milk  | cola      | mirinda | coffee     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | documentary | martial-arts | time-travel   | epic |

