.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-8::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: mirinda, water, cola, lemonade, hot-chocolate
The people have 5 different hobbies: drawing, magic-tricks, woodworking, filmmaking, photography
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking water##1
7. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage     | water | mirinda       | hot-chocolate | lemonade | cola    |
| Hobby   | filmmaking   | photography | woodworking  | magic-tricks     | drawing |

