.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-9::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, blend, aristoff, siglo, prince
There 5 different types of food: cherry, zucchini, pear, lemon, watermelon
1. the person eating pear is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
2. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
3. the blend-smoker is on the far right##1
4. the siglo-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
6. the prince-smoker is the person eating zucchini##1
7. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3       |      4      |    5    |
| Cigar         | siglo | dunhill | aristoff | prince | blend |
| Food   | pear       | lemon   | watermelon         | zucchini   | cherry   |

