.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-12::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: mystery, thriller, crime, family, martial-arts
5 different games are played: bridge, poker, snooker, domino, billiard
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person playing poker##1
2. the person watching family movies is the person playing billiard##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the far right##1
5. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
6. the person playing domino is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
7. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3     |    4    |    5    |
| Movie-Genre    | mystery | family          | crime    | martial-arts | thriller  |
| Game   | snooker  | billiard | bridge | domino | poker |

