.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-13::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, october, august, july, september
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, bolivar, prince, siglo, bluemaster
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
2. the prince-smoker is on the far right##1
3. the bolivar-smoker is the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is the prince-smoker##1
5. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
6. the person who's birthday is in july is in the middle##1
7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |    4     |    5    |
| Birthday   | august | march      | july | october | september |
| Cigar     | siglo  | bolivar | chaman     | bluemaster     | prince  |

