3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far right##1
6. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
7. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |     3      |   4    |    5     |
| Hobby           | photography     | hiking | gardening | traveling  | card-games |
| Flower   | dahlia | bellflower               | begonia     | balloon-flower | orchid |

