.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-17::.
There 5 different types of food: orange, pumpkin, plum, watermelon, zucchini
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, badminton, rowing, lacrosse, snowboarding
1. the person eating plum is on the right of the person eating orange##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person eating plum##1
3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person eating orange##1
4. the person eating orange is the person who's sport is badminton##1
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in the middle##1
6. the person eating watermelon is the person who's sport is rowing##1
7. the person eating pumpkin is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |  3   |    4    |   5    |
| Food   | orange   | plum    | zucchini | watermelon   | pumpkin |
| Sport     | badminton | basketball | lacrosse | rowing | snowboarding    |

