.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-18::.
There 5 different types of food: apricot, zucchini, cauliflower, raspberry, lime
There are 5 different favourite colors: lilac, turquise, chestnut, brown, fuchsia
1. the person who likes brown is in the middle##1
2. the person eating apricot is the person who likes brown##1
3. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
4. the person eating lime is the person who likes fuchsia##1
5. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
6. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
7. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4      |    5     |
| Food   | zucchini   | raspberry  | apricot | lime | cauliflower  |
| Color         | lilac | chestnut | brown  | fuchsia    | turquise |

