.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-19::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: house, reggae, folk, r&b, dubstep
House: modern, colonial, palace, gothic-revival, futuristic
1. the colonial house is on the right of the fan of folk##1
2. the fan of r&b is on the far right##1
3. the gothic-revival house is on the far left##1
4. the palace house is the fan of r&b##1
5. the fan of house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
6. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
7. the fan of house is on the right of the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |   4    |    5     |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep     | folk       | house     | reggae  | r&b  |
| House      | gothic-revival | modern | colonial | futuristic | palace |

