.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-20::.
City: liverpool, boston, colone, marseilles, edinburgh
There are 5 different nationalities: egyptian, canadian, polish, colombian, american
1. the canadian is in the middle##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the american##1
3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the egyptian##1
4. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
5. the polish is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
6. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |    3    |      4      |   5    |
| City   | boston | edinburgh | colone | liverpool | marseilles |
| Nationality           | american | colombian  | canadian    | egyptian  | polish   |

 